title: Production of creamery butter in Canada 2019
summary: The graph shows the Production of creamery in Tonnes Canada during 2019 .
There are several peaks and dips throughout the year .
The maximum value of Production has been recorded for September , and the minimum value has been recorded for August .
gold: This connected line graph provides an overview of the amount of creamery butter produced in Canada in the year 2019 . Production for the product peaked in Jan 2020 and the lowest production month was Aug . There is a steep dip in the graph as summer approaches , but production picks up again from September .
